tion/2034669670104557076"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIqPiFiLni2Pl4EAMaCTExOTM4MTkwMSCrr+HPBjAAONMIQAhyEzIwMzQ2Njk2NzAxMDQ1NTcwNzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1777989360.868536", "card_id": "Q_1943973749872367019", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么弥勒佛成了压轴的佛?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8a56edd021abaca1002bdf33ecb1b7c4_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "200 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1943973749872367019"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIqPiFiLni2Pl4EAMaCTExNjM2MzE0OCCDybnFBjAAOIgBQAlyEzE5NDM5NzM3NDk4NzIzNjcwMTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1777989360.868763", "card_id": "Q_2032557528245073398", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 143}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "浙江 81 岁老人 10 年还清 2077 万债务，她是如何做到的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2026 年 4 月 27 日，96 岁的陈金英老人在《浙江日报》刊发署名文章，回忆了自己从 81 岁到 91 岁、用十年时间还清 2077 万元债务的经历。 面对「诚信奶奶」和「道德模范」的称呼，老人这样回应：「我这一辈子没做什么惊天动地的大事，不过是守住了做人的底线。」 陈金英是浙江丽水人。53 岁那年，闲不住的她用积蓄租下三间民房，买来二手缝纫机，开始生产中老年羽绒服。品牌取名「老太太」，没有广告，她就抱着衣服走进敬老院、社区公园，一件件让人试穿。 生意最好的时候，年销售额突破千万元。陈金英坚持每年拿出利润的 30% 做公益：现金 57 万元，羽绒服直接送到敬老院和孤儿院。「自己小时候穿过补丁衣，知道冷是什么滋味。」她说。81 岁背上 2077 万元债务，卖掉厂房存货街头摆摊十年，96 岁奶奶回应「10 年还清债务」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c87de7d53ef0894461de629ed6c58352.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "192 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "ht